snippet.title: SUPER MARIO 3D WORLD - Launch Trailer (Wii U)
snippet.description:
Official Store: http://ow.ly/r2COS
SUPER MARIO 3D WORLD is released on 29th of November 2013, exclusively for Wii U.

Official website: http://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Wii-U/SUPER-MARIO-3D-WORLD-765385.html
The Wii U Difference: http://www.nintendo.co.uk/wiiudifference

Wii U on Facebook: https://facebook.com/WiiU.co.uk
Nintendo UK on Twitter: https://twitter.com/NintendoUK
